    <releaseNotes>'Merged PR 10425: VminSearch + VminTC supporting HERMES flow'
'Merged PR 10373: [PlatformService] Adds cache for APIs that return static values.'
'Merged PR 10354: [LSARaster] Adding filter to prevent repeated repair data'
'Merged PR 10341: [LSARaster] Adds ability to raster multiple slices/modules'
'Merged PR 9787: Query IsPatternAnAmble from pattern fail data (Prime 13)'
'Merged PR 9773: Merged PR 9729: Fixing broken links and wiki generation process'
'Merged PR 9718: Simplifying the FunctionalService's not-yet-deployed interfaces.'</releaseNotes>
